Package entities

Class MenuItems

java.lang.Object
entities.MenuItems
public class MenuItems extends Object
Represents a menu item in a restaurant's menu, from the Customer's view.
Version:
August 2024
Author:
Kfir Amoyal, Israel Ohayon, Yaniv Shatil, Noam Furman, Omri Heit, Eitan Zerbel

    • MenuItems

      public MenuItems(int item_id, int restaurant_id, String name, String description, double price, String category, ArrayList<String> possible_changes)
      Constructs a new MenuItems object with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      item_id - the unique ID of the menu item
      restaurant_id - the ID of the restaurant this item belongs to
      name - the name of the menu item
      description - a description of the menu item
      price - the price of the menu item
      category - the category of the menu item
      possible_changes - a list of possible modifications that can be made to the menu item
